To patch CVEs:
1. Download ncurses sources, extract them, and initialize git repository in the src root
2. Go to http://invisible-island.net/ncurses/#download_ncurses
3. Download the latest rollup of patches as a patch-X.X-YYYYMMDD.sh.gz file and ungzip the archive
4. Copy the extracted file into the src root, make it executable, and run it
5. Make a git commit to mark the rollup point
6. Download the remaining weekly patches from dev-patches.zip and unzip the archive
7. Apply all the git patches AFTER the rollup patch date in order
8. Make a git commit to mark the next rollup point